Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:33.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\fnArial\shad0\bord0\fax0.05\1c&H904A31&\pos(651,425)\frx0\fry5\frz356.5}Reflection Room 1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.27,0:01:36.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They finally let us go...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:39.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My neck hurts after sleeping on that hard floor for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:44.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't we supposed to have the advantage after taking down Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:45.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you topless?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:47.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's with those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:49.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\an6\3c&HFFFFFF&\be1\bord0.5\shad0\pos(1153,500)}Under First Contact Bridge {\fnNyala}-{\fn} Passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:50.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time they come we'll pay them back like we usually do to Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:53.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're ordinary students so we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:55.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's pretty weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:55.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:59.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ordinary students have never sent us to the reflection room before. {DING DING DING obvious clue is obvious}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.98,0:02:02.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Angel was keeping them in check?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:03.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:10.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,NPC actions are generally supposed to be models for how we should act, but their emotions are exactly like any normal human.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:13.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how weird someone acts, they're supposed to think it's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:17.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,you're saying this shows they can go farther than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:19.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That would seem to be how the acting student council president is reacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:22.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's more bothersome than Angel. She never turned the tables on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:24.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Yurippe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:25.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take him down with sex appeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:27.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of sex appeal do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:30.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? Have you seen these?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:32.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell just from your shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:34.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that's the same as touching them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.27,0:02:36.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Their absolutely exquisite form?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:37.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:38.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How shallow{\fnNyala}-{\fn}minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:46.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how should we proceed from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:46.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\an6\3c&HFFFFFF&\be1\bord0.5\shad3\pos(1151,502)}Anti{\fnNyala}-{\fn}Angel Operations Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.11,0:02:47.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to decide, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:52.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll experiment a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:55.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, attend classes and do whatever you want during them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:58.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try not to get in the way of the ordinary students.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all. Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.52,0:03:03.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:05.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:07.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:09.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that pretty valuable equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:11.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you giving it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:12.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:16.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel won't get in the way anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:19.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night was proof of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:22.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the problem is the acting student council president.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:25.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What will he do if we screw around with the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\an6\3c&HFFFFFF&\be1\bord0.5\shad0\pos(1153,502)}Study Block A — Classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eating snacks in the middle of class...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:36.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:37.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just ate one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:42.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd ever eat snacks in class like I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:44.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it gets through, it's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:45.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:47.58,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Are you serious? {TK}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:49.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Riichi, chitoi, dora, dora, oyaman.
Comment: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:49.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Note: That's 12,000 Hisako's way. 3,000 from TK and Matsushita, 6,000 from Fujimaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:51.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! It's all going to Hisako!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:52.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wild heaven. {TK}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:53.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Losing to a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:57.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You lot there, could you be a little quieter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:03:59.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:00.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:01.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I need the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:02.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:03.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:09.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's playing a student that needs to go to the bathroom every minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:10.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:12.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:14.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just sitting here's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:16.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, look over there. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:31.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:32.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:34.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:37.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:40.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes Naoi Ayato{\fnNyala}-{\fn}sama.{FOTC: 直井　文人. Naoi Ayato.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:41.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I need the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:41.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:46.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:00.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:03.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you can't hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:04.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:06.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take him to the reflection room. {should we maybe make this detention room?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:11.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you telling me to reflect on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:15.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were blatantly sleeping in the middle of class,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:18.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and then you threatened an innocent student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:20.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nerve asking that.{FOTC: (Comment) The student he threatened looks kind of... happy. Rape fantasies much?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite commendable, in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:24.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:27.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, are you running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:28.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:30.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here! Come right at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:31.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you're going?! {FOTC: (Comment) Oh, Noda. He's not running away. You're getting dragged away.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:39.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there really any point in keeping this up? {good shot}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:46.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\an6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1\bord1\shad3\pos(1153,502)}Main Dining Hall 3rd Floor — Rear
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:11.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:14.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:16.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:20.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, it's not even lunch yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:21.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:28.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The cafeteria has this ridiculously hot Mapo tofu that no one dares order.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:32.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I tried some, it was surprisingly good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:34.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:40.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about I... treat... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:43.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:46.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh okay, let's go!{FOTC: Tenshi~~~}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:49.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\an6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1\bord1\shad3\pos(1153,502)}Main Dining Hall Interior
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:51.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It really does look scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:54.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So freaking hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:58.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you're normally supposed to eat this with rice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:58.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:00.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Really"? Isn't this way too hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really. It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:03.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:06.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:11.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's not that you particularly like hot food, just that Mapo tofu is your favorite food?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:14.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:18.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I like Mapo tofu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:21.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even if you ask me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I never realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:29.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:32.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing at this time of day?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:34.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:35.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:38.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eating during breaktime is a violation of school regulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:43.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, it's a violation of school regulations...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:44.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:48.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistaking that she knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:50.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty scary what her favorite food can do to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:53.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:58.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:04.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply eating Mapo tofu during breaktime shouldn't warrant this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:07.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And where is this, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:08.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:09.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:10.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this isn't the time to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:15.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What else can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:17.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't this seem strange to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:20.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Throwing us into this jailroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:22.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to reflect on our actions, so there's no helping that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:23.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Still!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:26.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you sleep in this sort of situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:31.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:37.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She seriously went to sleep.{FOTC: かわゆーい!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:55.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:55.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,An earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:08:58.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:09:00.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're here to save—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:02.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, we're trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:09.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:11.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Piece of trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:17.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...shi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:19.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:21.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:23.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:26.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:30.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear me out and believe what I'm about to tell you, Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:34.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Naoi Ayato isn't an NPC.{FOTC: Naoi Ayato}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:36.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:38.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a human just like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:40.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:40.81,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:44.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As the former vice{\fnNyala}-{\fn}president, he was supposed to be a paragon of student life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:49.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If that were the case, he should have accepted his life and disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:53.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I discovered that he'd been beating up ordinary students under the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:58.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He acted like an exemplary student publicly, but in the shadows he was doing terrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how he maintained his balance in this world. {check}{FOTC: Good.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:02.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:07.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And when Angel lost her position, he obtained the freedom to do what he wants with this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:12.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what his objective is yet, but we've started battle against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:16.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a terrible fight like you've never seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:23.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He knows we won't harm ordinary students, so he's using them as shields and hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:26.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to submit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:29.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's turned into a one{\fnNyala}-{\fn}sided massacre.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:33.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Our friends are falling one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:37.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Angel's been imprisoned somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:42.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We went to the reflection room to find her, but she wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:46.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they put her in a different place, one not so easy to release her from.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:52.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And so I thought, maybe you're with her right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:54.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:56.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get Angel out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:11:01.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We need her to stop this terrible fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:02.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to the grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:09.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading out now too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:11.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:15.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:17.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:19.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:21.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My friends are in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:23.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a strange thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:25.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we the ones in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:27.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know that well enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:29.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:43.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard Skill: Hand Sonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:47.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get through the door with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No good, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:57.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't create it with offense in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:59.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's meant for self{\fnNyala}-{\fn}defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:00.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Self{\fnNyala}-{\fn}defense?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:01.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't create it with...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:07.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember when we first met?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:10.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You stabbed me through the heart and killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:12.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you asked something weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:16.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I mistook you for an enemy because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:19.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have my memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:22.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't really have any reason to fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:24.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I still had my memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:28.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't asked you that stupid question...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:32.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'd be your friend in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:33.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:35.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if there are, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:36.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are none.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:39.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there were, they'd all disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:52.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who befriends her would live a normal school life and eventually disappear from this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:56.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:58.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:03.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just too sad, too pitiful... {FOTC: She's so pitiful, so powerless...}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:04.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of system is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:09.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand sonic, version 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:14.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a thinner form for higher speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:18.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Version 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:23.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inelegant, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:24.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't open the door with this either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have any other forms?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:30.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, version 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:37.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to shape it like a flower, but maybe it looks too cute? {FOTC: I tried making it look like a flower, but is it actually cute?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.49,0:13:40.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it looks pretty threatening...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:42.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That might work...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you try something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:50.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand sonic version 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.19,0:13:56.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Version 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Version 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:02.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:12.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:33.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is this....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:50.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:57.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:02.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Running straight to me first...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:03.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:05.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time for jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:10.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get out of there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:12.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I broke the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.71,0:15:15.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd made it tough enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:19.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I order you as the acting student council president to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:23.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana, you see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:25.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that this is just not right, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:27.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand sonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:30.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you rebelling against God?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For I am God.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:35.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Has he lost it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:37.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:42.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did none of you realize that this is a world that chooses its God?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:45.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember when I was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:47.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone here had a cruel life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:49.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:51.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that is what gives you the right to be God.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:56.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As one who lived through such a terrible life, I also earned the right to become God.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:59.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I have reached that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:02.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And what will you do after becoming God?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:03.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bestow eternal rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:05.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,On us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By massacring us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:09.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Only because you resisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:17.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You all had the right to become God, but you bound yourselves to your lives and kept struggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,God has been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:22.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And so I will bestow rest upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:25.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:30.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you intend to do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:34.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:38.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to rest in peace now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:41.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember Iwasawa's guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:45.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In her past life, she was robbed of her voice and her dream to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:48.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She died miserably, with a terrible family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:52.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But her dream was granted in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:53.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And so she disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:55.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She was able to rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:02.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And now you're going to follow her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:04.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a nice dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:06.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know my past!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:08.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:15.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't spend all that time preparing just to remove Angel from power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:17.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hypnotism.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:24.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:27.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to enter a blissful dream now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:31.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in this world, you can dream of a happy place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:32.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:34.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:36.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:37.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:47.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:50.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:52.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make such happy faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:55.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:58.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I let you die one by one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:17:59.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,One by one...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:03.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,until none of you were left!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:04.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:07.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy you're my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:08.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:11.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:13.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:19.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get rid of her with some fake memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.17,0:18:23.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Our lives were real!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:25.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single moment of them were fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:27.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone lived the best they could!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We carved those memories into ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:32.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Memories of living as hard as we could!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:36.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what kind they were, they're the life we led!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:39.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Erasing them in the blink of an eye like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:45.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't your life also real to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:50.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:19:01.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We were born to a famous potter,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:03.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,my older twin brother and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:03.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sign: Naoi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.39,0:19:07.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother showed talent from a young age.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:09.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They proclaimed him the heir to the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:14.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I on the other hand, stayed in my room every day, playing alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:19.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,living a meaningless life, getting no attention from anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:22.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"The one who died was you."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:25.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what they told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:26.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:29.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am alive and I am my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:32.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I traded places with my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:35.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:39.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then a meaningful life began.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:45.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Removed from the world to recover from the injury, my rehabilitation was strict training.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:47.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is shameful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:49.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Days of father yelling angrily at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:52.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Making garbage like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:55.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My training grew more and more severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:58.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother was just too far from my reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:03.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I persevered to turn my life into something meaningful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:08.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to go back to a life of playing alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:11.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won an award at an exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:14.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing compared to what my brother could have done,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:16.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but it was the best result I could have produced in my position.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:18.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:20.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.62,0:20:21.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:23.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It is absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:26.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bring me shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:28.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly. What are these results?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:30.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:34.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would stay with my father and continue my training,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:37.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and then become the best potter in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:43.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My father became bedridden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:45.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They said there was no hope for recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't spin the wheel anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:53.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't teach me pottery, and he couldn't scold me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:58.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I fed him, he would smile kindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:01.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All meaning to my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:05.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost it all since I couldn't maintain the workshop, and I couldn't be independent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:09.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My life under the care of my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:12.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,God!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:14.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\pos(640,310)\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&HBB&\blur4\shad0}The one who died was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:18.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really was the one who died that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:22.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my brother who had worked so hard every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:24.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And here, I'm my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.39,0:21:27.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was always just my brother and father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:29.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My life was a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,0:21:32.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was not in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:36.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life was real too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.68,0:21:38.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You worked hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:40.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You struggled as hard as you could!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:41.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:43.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:45.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:47.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:50.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, will you acknowledge me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:52.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Me as I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:55.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What else could I acknowledge?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:58.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The one in my arms is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.14,0:21:59.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Not here"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:01.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no one else but you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:06.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just persimmons, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:10.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! I beat my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:17.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking? It's a persimmon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:21.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But good job, Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.81,0:22:27.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were the words I wanted to hear the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.41,0:22:31.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,200)}Ayato
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:30.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those words that acknowledged my existence.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< preview >
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:18.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.63,0:24:19.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.19,0:24:19.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's stupidly huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.00,0:24:20.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Carnival of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.28,0:24:20.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go with Tornado?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.39,0:24:22.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}O! S!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.11,0:24:21.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,God cannot fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.39,0:24:21.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically he's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.83,0:24:23.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Overdrive is passive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.22,0:24:23.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be trouble if you make light of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.23,0:24:23.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You can regain your lost memories too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.27,0:24:24.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Onii{\fnNyala}-{\fn}chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.77,0:24:24.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.85,0:24:27.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't die...
