Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.29,0:00:26.79,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I open my eyes again, to a sleepy morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:33.55,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I tighten the tie around my neck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:36.80,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}When I pass through the door of the classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:46.40,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I puff my chest out with a little bit of pride
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:53.53,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A wind that blows past everyday life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:56.86,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I thought I heard it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:01:02.79,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I thought I felt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:06.83,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It started to shake within my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.96,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I felt it would come now
