Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:41.31,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,500)}Everyone becomes alone someday
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:48.99,ed_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,500)}They live on only in memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:56.66,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,500)}So I can laugh with my heart, even in this loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.66,0:24:04.13,ed_english2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,500)}I will fight
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:11.80,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,500)}I will show no tears
